the users folder includes the following tables:

* users
* roles
* accounts
* users_roles
* sessions


the items folder includes the following tables:

* item_categories
* item_brands
* items
* item_category assignments
* item_stocks
* item_restocks

the purchase folder includes the following tables:

* suppliers
* purchases
* purchase_payments
* purchase_item_stocks


the sales folder includes the following tables:

* sales
* sales_payments
* sale_item_restocks

